<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>373</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>zhǔ kàn gù 迦南373</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ kàn gù zhǔ kàn gù, yī shēng dōu méng zhǔ kàn gù,
 yǒu duō shǎo nán wàng shì, zāo yù xiǎn jìng huà zhù fú.
 zhǔ kàn gù zhǔ kàn gù. yǒu duō shǎo rén jì niàn zhǔ.
 zhǔ kàn gù zhǔ kàn gù. yǒu duō shǎo rén róng yào zhǔ.</lyrics>
</song>